snippet.title: Sonic Adventure but it's own Sonic fan game
snippet.description:
I have now created a tutorial for my Sonic fan game. 

Also, I imported some levels from Sonic Adventure. 

Now available on itch.io!

https://evilbritishguy.itch.io/sonic-and-the-hedgehogs
